{"md5":"791f43f8108f5ae7b65d21c48731a4a5","content":"\n\n\n<div id=\"outline-container-orga4bebdc\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"orga4bebdc\"><span class=\"section-number-2\">1</span> 前言</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-1\">\n<p>\n这里只讲在我的电脑上如何抓包而已\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-orgde3b8e2\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"orgde3b8e2\"><span class=\"section-number-2\">2</span> 抓802.11包</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-2\">\n<p>\nwireshark默认情况下无法抓取无线网络的管理包。我们可以通过配置无线网卡为monitor模式，来使用wireshark进行抓包。将网卡设为monitor会导致无法联网，如果在使用WiFi会比较麻烦，所以还是生成一个虚拟网卡来监听最好。对于无线网卡，使用 iw 来来代替iwconfig进行操作（使用ip估计不行）：\n</p>\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">iw dev wlan0 interface add mon0 <span class=\"built_in\">type</span> monitor</span><br><span class=\"line\">ip link <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> mon0 up</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</div>\n<p>\n之后就可以使用Wireshark抓包了\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org9bcf812\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"org9bcf812\"><span class=\"section-number-2\">3</span> 抓802.1q包</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-3\">\n<p>\n电脑默认是抓不到带有vlan tag的包的，所以要设定一个VLAN网口\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org7223615\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"org7223615\"><span class=\"section-number-2\">4</span> FAQ</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-4\">\n</div><div id=\"outline-container-orgd208068\" class=\"outline-3\">\n<h3 id=\"orgd208068\"><span class=\"section-number-3\">4.1</span> 1200Mbps的速度是真的吗？</h3>\n<div class=\"outline-text-3\" id=\"text-4-1\">\n<p>\n一般是指2.4G的的速度300Mbps，5G的速度867Mbps，加起来大约有1200Mbps\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org625e48f\" class=\"outline-3\">\n<h3 id=\"org625e48f\"><span class=\"section-number-3\">4.2</span> </h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-orgb7cf5b2\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"orgb7cf5b2\"><span class=\"section-number-2\">5</span> 参考</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-5\">\n<ul class=\"org-ul\">\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aneasystone.com/archives/2016/08/wireless-analysis-one-monitoring.html\">实战无线网络分析（篇一）无线监听</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/VLAN_(%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87)\">Vlan设置</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\nLast Updated 2017-04-22 六 22:05.<br>Render by <a href=\"https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-renderer-org\">hexo-renderer-org</a> with <a href=\"http://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/\">Emacs</a> 25.2.1 (<a href=\"http://orgmode.org\">Org</a> mode 9.0.5)\n"}
